Barry Lyttle has pleaded guilty to recklessly causing grievous bodily harm to his brother Patrick . 
  Patrick was left in a coma after he was allegedly punched by his brother in Kings Cross on January 3 . 
  Barry has been given a 13-month suspended jail sentence in Sydney court on Friday . 
  Patrick spent six days in an induced coma after the alleged attack . 
  He has called on the charges against his brother to be dropped . 
 